  "comment": "As part of our Platinum Line we now present the next generation of LED PAR spotlights. Tri-LED 3 in 1 is now the new system and leaves nothing to be desired. The new lens system allows RGB colour mixing even before the lens and creates a ready mixed colour when the light is emitted.\n3 Watt Tri-LEDs provide an enormous brightness that is equal to that of a conventional 300 Watt spotlight. Equipped with 2 brackets, the lamp can also be used as a floor spot. Its compact size allows for unobtrusive use at all events.",
